                        <interp inst="t18370703-name-613" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN PAWLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. On the 12th of June I saw the prisoner sitting on a barrow, at Mr. Colson's house—he said there was a drawer in Mr. Colson's where he could get 9<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. or 10<hi rend="italic">l</hi>—I had known him about two years.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> It is false—I never told him so.</p>
